  // ============================================================
  // connection + offline queue
  // ============================================================
  // All chore mutations are write-ahead to this queue, then the queue
  // drains via flushQueue. The user's tap is durable in localStorage
  // BEFORE the network is touched — backgrounding the app mid-flight
  // can't lose work. Queue items carry a `loud` flag: silent by default
